summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plats 14E, 15W, and 23E, pages 60, 61 and 62, of the official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, (Ordinance 86300), to rezone certain properties in the University District area from RD 5000 to RS 5000, from RMH 350 to RM 800, and from RMV 200 to RMH 350, and adopting certain findings and conclusions of the Council regarding such rezoning (Petition of University District Community Council, C.F. 280586, Hearing Examiner No. X-74-202).
